OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FQuite cloudy
OL,6,Fat first with some rain, perhaps heavy
OL,7,Fover Orkney. Becoming sunny then clear
OL,8,Ffor Shetland overnight, cloudier but
OL,9,Fwith some clear spells possible for
OL,10,FOrkney and a chance of some showers.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FA chance of rain for Orkney
OL,13,Fearly on. Otherwise dry with good
OL,14,Fsunny spells for Shetland, quite
OL,15,Fcloudy for Orkney but some bright or
OL,16,Fsunny spells breaking out at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
