OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FA dry
OL,6,Ffew days with plenty of sunshine on
OL,7,FSunday and Monday, likely turning
OL,8,Fsomewhat cloudier on Tuesday but still
OL,9,Fsome sunny spells. Winds will be light.
